# Standard .gitignore for jd4883 / expectedbehaviors Helm chart repos.
# Prefer glob patterns over static paths so nested charts (e.g. deploy/helm/**)
# and future cruft are caught automatically. To keep a normally-ignored file in
# one repo, add a negation below the relevant block, e.g.  !poetry.lock

# ---- OS / editor cruft ----
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/

# ---- Helm: vendored subcharts & packaged archives (resolved in CI) ----
charts/
**/charts/
*.tgz

# ---- Lock files (Chart.lock, requirements.lock, *.lock) ----
# Helm deps are resolved at render/CI time; never commit lockfiles here.
*.lock
**/*.lock

# ---- Terraform (immutable: never commit state, provider cache, or lock) ----
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
.terraform.lock.hcl
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example

# ---- AI / PR / review scratch — drafts that never belong in the repo ----
PR_*.md
PR_*.txt
PR_BODY*
REVIEW_CONSISTENCY*.md
*CONSISTENCY-REPORT*
migration.md
MIGRATION.md
RUN-TO-STRIP*.md
*_upstream_values.txt
.cruft.json
